<p>The first theme is a highly <a href="./pages/musiccomp.html#2214">syncopated jaunty melody</a></p>
<p>A big image for bold music that depicts a big, bold planet!</p>
<p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jupiter">Mighty Jupiter - the king of the planets</a> (<a href="https://www.wikipedia.org">Wikipedia</a>) </p>
