<p>Horns ‘herald’ too. Here they announce the arrival of Callisto, another of the four Galilean moons</p>
<p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ganymede_(moon)">This is Ganymede</a> (<a href="https://www.wikipedia.org">Wikipedia</a>) </p>
<p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ganymede_(moon)">Ganymede</a> is the largest moon in the Solar System</p>
<p>Where did they go? Jupiter is a prankster</p>
